data.description: Welcome home! This wonderful 3-bed & 2-bath property harmoniously blends comfort and charm. Offering a 2-car garage and a desert landscape. Discover an inviting layout showcasing a formal living room w/fireplace, a bright dining room adjacent to the kitchen, and a versatile family room w/French doors to the back. Plantation shutters, vaulted ceilings, designer paint, and a mix of tile & wood-look flooring enhance the home's relaxed ambiance. The kitchen boasts built-in appliances, granite counters, ample wood cabinets, a pantry, and a breakfast bar. Main bedroom is a private retreat with a full bathroom. Den has a double-door entry. You'll love the spacious backyard featuring an open patio, cozy deck, & a sparkling play pool & Spa for year-round enjoyment! Don't miss this gem!
